		<item>
			<title>Version 1.1.2</title>
			<description>
			<![CDATA[
				<h1>New features</h1>

				<ul>
				    <li>Updated to Oculus Runtime 1.14.0</li>
				    <li>Updated to OpenVR 1.0.7</li>
				    <li>Third-party motion controllers with physical buttons/thumbsticks are now supported (i.e. Razer Hydra)</li>
				</ul>


				<h1>Bug fixes</h1>

				<ul>
				    <li>Reduce jitter in games with tracking prediction issues (#584)</li>
				</ul>
			]]>
			</description>
